## Nature of this fork

This is **not** a wholesale mirror. Only selected skills and documentation are
carried; the rest of upstream's tree is intentionally absent. The relationship
is managed by a documented selective-sync strategy (upstream `remote` for
fetching, a local override layer in `docs/agents/*` for this fork's own
conventions). See ADR-0001 for the full rationale.

